    "created_at": "2015-02-27T23:31:45Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-02-27T23:31:45Z",
    "body": "Testing this [branch](https://github.com/atom/atom-shell/pull/1176) with some example code, run-from-tray behavior is pretty trivial to implement:\n\n``` javascript\nhostWindow.on('close', (e) => {\n  if (hostWindow.forceClose) return;\n  e.preventDefault();\n  hostWindow.hide();\n});\n\napp.on('before-quit', () => {\n  hostWindow.forceClose = true;\n});\n\napp.on('activate-with-no-open-windows', () => {\n  hostWindow.show();\n});\n```\n\nThoughts @zcbenz?\n"
  },
